@startuml
!theme plain

skinparam node {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor Black
}

' ==================== MAIN NODES ====================

node "Client Device" as Client {
  [Web Browser] as Browser
  database "Local Storage" as Storage
}

node "Web Server" as WebServer {
  [Nginx] as Nginx
  [Flask Application] as Flask
  database "Session Cache" as Cache
}

node "Database Server" as DBServer {
  database "MySQL Database" as MySQL
}

node "Backup Server" as Backup {
  database "Backup Storage" as Backups
}

' ==================== CONNECTIONS ====================

Client -right-> WebServer : **HTTP/HTTPS**\nPort 80/443
note on link
REST API with JWT
JSON Data Exchange
end note

WebServer -right-> DBServer : **MySQL**\nPort 3307
note on link
PyMySQL Driver
Connection Pooling
end note

DBServer -right-> Backup : **SSH/RSYNC**\nPort 22
note on link
Daily Backups
Encrypted Transfer
end note

' Internal connections
Nginx -down-> Flask : WSGI\nPort 5000
Flask -down-> Cache : Redis\nPort 6379

' ==================== ARTIFACTS ====================

artifact "React App" as React {
  [Static Files]
  [Components]
}

artifact "Python Backend" as Python {
  [API Routes]
  [Services]
  [Models]
}

artifact "Database Schema" as Schema {
  [16 Tables]
  [Views]
}

React --> Browser
Python --> Flask
Schema --> MySQL

' ==================== NOTES ====================

note top of Client
**Client Side**
• Modern Browser
• JavaScript
• Local Storage
end note

note top of WebServer
**Application Layer**
• Ubuntu 20.04
• 4GB RAM
• Nginx + Flask
end note

note top of DBServer
**Database Layer**
• MySQL 9.50
• 8GB RAM
• SSD Storage
end note

note top of Backup
**Backup Layer**
• Daily Backups
• 30-Day Retention
• Encrypted
end note
@enduml
